# Project Initialization: SGH-V1 Infrastructure & Data Models

This plan covers the initial setup of the "Sistema Integral de Habilitaciones" (SGH-V1) based on the provided "Master Document". We will set up the containerized environment and the core data models.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The project structure will be created directly in the root of the repository (`c:\Users\Admin\GitHub\SGH-V1\`). This includes `backend/` and `frontend/` directories.

## Proposed Changes

### Infrastructure

#### [NEW] [docker-compose.yml](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/docker-compose.yml)
Define three services:
- `db`: PostgreSQL 15+ container with a persistent volume.
- `backend`: FastAPI application container.
- `frontend`: Simple `nginx` container to serve static HTML/JS/CSS files.

#### [NEW] [.env](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/.env)
Store environment variables for the database (USER, PASSWORD, NAME) and security secrets (JWT SECRET).

---

### Backend

#### [NEW] [Dockerfile](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/backend/Dockerfile)
Python 3.11 image, installation of dependencies from `requirements.txt`, and entrypoint for `uvicorn`.

#### [NEW] [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/backend/requirements.txt)
Include: `fastapi`, `uvicorn`, `sqlalchemy`, `alembic`, `pydantic-settings`, `psycopg2-binary` (or `asyncpg`), `python-jose`, `passlib`.

#### [NEW] [app/main.py](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/backend/app/main.py)
Initial FastAPI entry point with basic routes and dependency injection for the database.

#### [NEW] [app/db/models/](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/backend/app/db/models/)
Implement the following entities using SQLAlchemy 2.0:
- `Persona`, `Empresa`, `Documento`, `Estado`, `Habilitacion`, `Alerta`, `Usuario`, `Auditoria`.

#### [NEW] [app/core/config.py](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/backend/app/core/config.py)
Configuration management using `pydantic-settings`.

---

### Frontend

#### [NEW] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/frontend/index.html)
Initial landing page with Bootstrap 5 setup.

#### [NEW] [js/api.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/GitHub/SGH-V1/frontend/js/api.js)
Base wrapper for `fetch()` to handle authentication and standard API responses.

